Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻过所有的杂志也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 与我相称的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都无法 讨得你的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你失望了 对不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点都不像我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  别用那种冷冷的眼神望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我照着自己的步调去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我很快就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.39,0:22:38.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.86,0:22:44.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.31,0:22:49.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手寻找温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.57,0:22:55.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  奇迹也一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.92,0:23:08.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.80,0:23:19.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 现在 在我手中 有诞生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.56,0:23:27.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神饱满  也不能   太过勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.94,0:23:32.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.36,0:23:43.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起来  培育茁壮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.45,0:00:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.29,0:00:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.09,0:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要说到秋天寻宝的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年侦探团要向暗号挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.02,0:01:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮、星星和太阳的秘密(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.12,0:01:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在要去的别墅真的藏有宝藏吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.68,0:01:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.14,0:01:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要用你们的智慧去找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我们少年侦探团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的宝藏都会属于我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.34,0:02:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.05,0:02:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是之前叫我买的那堆玩具吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们听见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪灰原那家伙才不想跟来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你最近还很慷慨 这辆车也是新买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.75,0:02:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成博士你做了什么东西来打劫银行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经病 我怎么可能会那么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是这个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.93,0:02:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识的朋友的公司找我帮他们开发新玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了一大笔的合约金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人变声器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士今天早上也送给我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个假面超人变声器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人变声器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.09,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以录自己的声音 然后转变成其它的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是假面超人的新产品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.94,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和蝴蝶结变声器一样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.44,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 你一直看不起的我的发明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要全国各地销售了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的是博士叔父的别墅吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我叔父叫做阿笠栗介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这一带有名的大富豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.46,0:03:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在50年前把一大笔财产藏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.93,0:03:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次我想借助你们少年侦探团的智慧帮我找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:04:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不是博士事先来这里将宝物藏起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士是不会骗我们小孩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不笨嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从这间房间开始找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.42,0:04:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.09,0:04:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的叔父就是画中那个男人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.77,0:04:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.86,0:04:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来博士的叔父的确是个有钱人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.56,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 画中背后的暖炉和这里的一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.35,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说特地请人来这里画肖像画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够这样做的 就是有钱人家的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.02,0:05:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这是叔父病逝一年前请一位年轻画家画的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.79,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起的那位女性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是为了照顾叔父而搬来这里一起住的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是叔父唯一信赖的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在这附近的小学教书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.62,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父死后她也回娘家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.06,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的50年这里都没有人来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里东西还真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些书籍 餐具…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为叔父的遗嘱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间别墅在我死后50年之内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.08,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要改变任何东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然并没有什么财产留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也决定下个月要拆掉它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你想趁被拆之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.60,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这布满灰尘的别墅中和小鬼们玩寻宝游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.73,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱翻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.52,0:06:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心留意周围 一定可以发现到什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.38,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 例如我的脚下刻的那些怪字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.74,0:06:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,モ ザ リ サ ワ ソ デ ル
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英文吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 一定是阿拉伯文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就算是新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.01,0:06:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.21,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这次连新一也被我的问题给难倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.74,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪 我用了三天三夜想出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果博士是说你藏的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.67,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在对面寝室的床底下找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有打开来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.32,0:07:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用布盖上然后推进去了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有劳你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.05,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我在想的是这个别墅的另外一个谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一个谜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这东西有何看法 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.83,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是一个普通的一元硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在床边捡到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我掉的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面全是灰尘 而且附近没有它滚过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这枚一元硬币的首次发行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是40年前的1955年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.97,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而它竟然在这别墅里 还布满灰尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.02,0:08:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…这无人的别墅 有人擅自闯入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.94,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不止进来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里住过一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是个手指非常灵活的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.27,0:08:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住过…手指灵活…老人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然博士拿一枚一元硬币出来和那个硬币比较看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.47,0:08:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做比较… 哪里不一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.94,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然比我的硬币还薄 而且还小了一圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一元硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.55,0:08:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从原来的硬币削出来变成缩水的一元硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的手工非常厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个「国」字也变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道这是故意的还是失误的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过会用以前的那个「国」字 都是上了年纪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你怎么知道是住在这里的人做出来的东西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 的确是在这里做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.54,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是一边看书一边做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书本里面夹着制造硬币的金属片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些白头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.66,0:09:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且没有人可以在短时间之内刻出这样的一元硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就证明这个人长时间住在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.19,0:09:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 可能是消磨时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.44,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还不能肯定是不是只有一个老人住在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有小朋友的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子住过这里的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看这花瓶的底部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.51,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是小孩子乱画的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西我也有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.81,0:10:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这烛台的底下也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这盘子的背面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是个顽皮的小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.35,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是快去解开地板的暗号吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.33,0:10:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 叔父应该没有小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道住在这里的神秘老人是带着孩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「跳舞的人偶」吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞的人偶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指夏洛克·福尔摩斯小说里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.87,0:10:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些人偶排队跳舞的奇妙图案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.36,0:11:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得那是画成小孩子的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.19,0:11:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道这个也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶和烛台和盘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较里面的图案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边三个完全一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.52,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说这是个有规律的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.10,0:11:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.96,0:11:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你会读那些暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.52,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人的谜 一元硬币的谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是不明白越是兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心底压抑不住的好奇心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说侦探的血在沸腾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.17,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 我觉得这些图形 好像在哪里见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.45,0:12:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？ 你在哪看过 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起来想一想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板上写的那些暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.21,0:12:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要在那里偷懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.11,0:12:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,モ ザ リ サ ワ ソ デ ル
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.69,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不明白是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过通常这类的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.69,0:12:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多用前一个或后一个文字写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.97,0:12:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们试着退后一个文字读出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.50,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟…着…箭…头…走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着箭头走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们去找箭头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.41,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来这间房间的时候不是会先看到一个箭头吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那种东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看那个时钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时钟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时钟怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不觉得那6点半有点奇怪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是坏掉停下来而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们仔细看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的时钟如果是六点半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时针与分针应该是会分开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而它们却是重叠在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就表示有人故意移动过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.68,0:13:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是藏起宝藏的某个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.71,0:13:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说那个时钟的针就是第一个箭头吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来就是找那时钟的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有一堆扑克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到中间的黑桃A了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不知为何用图钉固定起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.19,0:13:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 A就是箭头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西洋棋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 这棋子的排列方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排列方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.37,0:14:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细一看就是箭头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.92,0:14:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面还黏上胶水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.82,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定没错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.78,0:14:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有箭头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.72,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是收藏宝物的人最伤脑筋的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看门对面的桌子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有三个点没有灰尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是证明上面原来放有东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指这掉到地上的飞机吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.05,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它照着痕迹放回桌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.16,0:15:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机指向床耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想宝物就在这床里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床的下面好像有东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定就是宝箱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确在桌子上放了架飞机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不记得把它弄倒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点打开 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.62,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.18,0:15:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用刀子割成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.44,0:15:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是收藏宝物的人想吓我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 博士是不会那样做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说这些玩具是博士藏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.29,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为了和你们在这里玩寻宝游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是博士在放好离开之后到我们来这里这段期间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有人来过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.99,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那家伙大概看到博士留下的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到寝室的宝箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后看到里面全是玩具后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恼羞成怒 用刀割烂它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士放在桌上的飞机会掉到地上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那个时候弄掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人为什么要来这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.33,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 可能是偶然经过好奇之下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.85,0:16:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就是为了找什么东西而来到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.97,0:16:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许和那些图案有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图案？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.64,0:16:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们发现的那些太阳 月亮 星星的诡异图案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.48,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那些是暗号？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.49,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.20,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.18,0:17:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这间别墅里真的有宝藏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 警方怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.26,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说大概是恶劣的小偷干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.96,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天会来调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.59,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家最好什么都不要碰 就这样离开比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 虽然对那些暗号很好奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想再弄乱现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.88,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.27,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出更多的暗号 然后找出宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.65,0:17:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 犯人可能还在附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张扑克牌后面也有暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.31,0:17:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我和步美找一楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太和光彦去找二楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太多疑了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又发现了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.27,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果后来又发现了7个暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑克牌 法文字典 唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.32,0:18:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机 酒杯 肖像画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.34,0:18:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.74,0:18:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来我听阿姨说过 叔父生前很喜欢这种娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有最先找到的3个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.27,0:19:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子 烛台 花瓶  一共10个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.44,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些东西放在这里也不知道是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有再长些一点的 像是文章之类的就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如日记或者信这类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.58,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信 就是信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了嘛 那个图形在哪里见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前阿姨曾给我看过 我完全忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的阿姨就是这画中的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说她以前当过小学老师的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.81,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那是五六年前的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说从10年前开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都有封没寄信人地址和名字的信寄给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很奇怪 所以阿姨拿给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.21,0:19:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得内容全部都是用平假名写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.99,0:20:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像「老师您好」「保重身体」之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是她的学生寄的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.52,0:20:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是 因为十年来一直都是用平假名写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的确很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.15,0:20:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些信和暗号有什么关系呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面全部都画着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.52,0:20:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那些平假名的信的四周 就像一些花纹一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那些信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为完全看不懂 所以去请教你爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.43,0:20:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 住在附近的一个推理小说家好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给爸爸看过了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.97,0:20:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小说家因为没有灵感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初不太高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他看到那些信以后 突然兴奋起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拿着那些信回到屋子里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没几分钟就出来了 然后这样对我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.06,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我把这封信交给你阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.88,0:21:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就像太阳一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你 我灰暗的心情被一扫而光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信里面写些什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是暗号的解读表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.23,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那个小说家发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些暗号都是平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.00,0:21:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 信的内容全是用平假名写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.66,0:21:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是指要用平假名去读四周的图案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.38,0:21:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来写那些信和画这里的暗号应该是同一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.08,0:21:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人为什么要写那些暗号给我阿姨呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是不想让阿姨以外的人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.36,0:21:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如他正在被某人跟踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.99,0:22:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 阿姨曾经说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.81,0:22:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个怪人经常偷她的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.73,0:22:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那家伙就是弄坏玩具的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.32,0:22:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个别墅果然不寻常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.44,0:23:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的有宝藏吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.01,0:23:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.17,0:23:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暗号 刻在地板上的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.42,0:24:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果将它们依照顺序串联起来的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.94,0:24:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷…骷髅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.93,0:24:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.87,0:24:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.48,0:24:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮、星星和太阳的秘密(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.88,0:24:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.29,0:24:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20元纸币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.07,0:24:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次终于要解开暗号了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.61,0:24:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.76,0:24:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
